{"about_the_game":"You\u2019ve barely escaped the chaos that consumed your hometown overnight. The friendly residents of Grimshire, an isolated mountain village, offer you a new home. Restore the cozy old farmhouse, and tend the fields. But beware, the plague is coming. The community must work together if they are to survive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238470/extras/Steam_banner_crops2.gif?t=1737047856\" /><br><br> <strong>Feed Them</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Keep the root cellar stocked, balance the needs of herbivores and carnivores.<br></li><li>Prevent food from rotting away by salting, pickling, drying, smoking, and canning.<br></li><li>Cultivate a field of crops, and plant an orchard of fruit and nut trees.<br></li><li>Tame wild critters and raise them for a steady supply of eggs, milk, and meat.<br></li><li>Forage for seeds, flowers, herbs, nuts, roots and berries.<br></li><li>Go fishing in nearby marshes, rivers, and lakes.</li></ul><strong>Be a part of the Community</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gather materials and construct village projects to strengthen the community.<br></li><li>Donate items for research and discover new methods to increase the odds of survival.<br></li><li>Befriend all the adorable villagers of Grimshire, and romance any of the 10 available partners.<br></li><li>Not everyone will survive the plague...</li></ul><strong>Explore the World</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dive deep in the mines of Grimshire valley, and root out every vein of ore.<br></li><li>Experience beautiful shifting dynamic seasons and weather.<br></li><li>Decorate your home and farm with a variety of furniture, fences, pathing stones, and more!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238470/extras/RootCellarStronger2.gif?t=1737047856\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asset